{"tid":502644,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌奶星連桌球冠軍都忍唔住發表迷雲言論","createTime":"2017-12-18T06:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T06:26:46.000Z","uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26a90d8981e0929d79788f6feb12e59b882ad317","tid":502644,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T06:09:31.000Z","msg":"英超車路士忠實球迷羅拔臣在今次賽事打出11Cue Century，追平傅家俊去屆封王的紀錄。他賽後表示今仗很難忘︰「極少在落後多局的劣勢反勝。很同情對手的處境，他一定很難受像世界末日，更不會想見到我慶祝的表情。這是尊重對手的表現，（阿仙奴主帥）雲格早前談到『日本相撲手取勝後不會慶祝，不能憑表情分辨出誰是勝方』，我認為這態度可取，改變了我。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c650dd993f4f5fd0a734c2542db7bfd0388a5976","tid":502644,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ddbb3b10a7ca0b6347cc6e0ef012fbdfa3db76","tid":502644,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贏左唔準慶祝, 輸左都唔準喊<br />\n<br />\n違反人性, 痴撚線"}]}